Mantle smiled at Epyon and nodded his head too when Prowl introduced them. 
He looked back at Prowl and Iron Raptor.

"Prowl is right, commander." He said, coming to Prowl's defence. "This won't 
take long, and won't take any botpower away from the battle. Cyndro can 
begin construction on his own. But we should discuss this in a safe place, 
follow me."

Mantle hovered up in the air and set off toward the Element. He hoped that 
the others would follow him, because discussion in the middle of a 
battlefield can be hard.
